### Test Inventory Endpoints
# Change the port number if you're not using 5285

### Get all inventory
GET http://localhost:5285/api/inventory

### Get inventory for specific product
GET http://localhost:5285/api/inventory?productId=1

### Get inventory for non-existent product (should return 404)
GET http://localhost:5285/api/inventory?productId=99999

###

### Test Order Endpoints

### Get order by ID
GET http://localhost:5285/api/orders/1

### Get non-existent order (should return 404)
GET http://localhost:5285/api/orders/99999

###
